@startuml popup_guide_and_theme_to_hud_mode_brightness_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Popup Guide And Theme To HUD Mode Brightness Signal Flow\n(HMI popup + navigation guide + cluster theme -> HUD mode and brightness)

participant "HMI popup bus" as Popup #F4F7FB
participant "Navigation route bus" as Nav #E8F0FE
participant "Cluster theme bus" as Theme #FCE8FF
participant "HUD\nwarning-render owner" as HUD #E8F7E8
participant "HUD state bus" as HudBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\nvisual readers" as Obs #FFF4CC

== HUD Inputs ==

Popup -> HUD : frmHmiPopupStateMsg\nPopupPriority / PopupActive
Nav -> HUD : frmNavigationRouteMsg\nGuideType
Theme -> HUD : frmClusterThemeMsg\nThemeMode / ClusterBrightness
activate HUD
HUD -> HUD : popup/guide/theme lease + hold windows
HUD -> HUD : if popup expired then\nPopupPriority = 0 / PopupActive = 0
HUD -> HUD : if guide expired then\nGuideType = 0
HUD -> HUD : if theme expired then\nThemeMode = 0 / Brightness = 18
HUD -> HUD : hudMode =\npopup active & priority>=5 ? 2 :\nguideType>0 ? 3 : 0
HUD -> HUD : if popupActive == 1 and brightness < 24\nthen brightness = 24
note right of HUD
Representative gating inputs
- PopupPriority / PopupActive
- GuideType
- ThemeMode
- ClusterBrightness
end note

== HUD Publish ==

HUD -> HudBus : frmHudStateMsg\nHudMode / HudGuideType / HudBrightness
note right of HUD
Representative outputs
- HudMode
- HudGuideType
- HudBrightness
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

HudBus -> Obs : HUD mode and brightness visibility /\nvisual observers
deactivate HUD

note over Popup, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Popup, guide, and theme context reach HUD
2. HUD applies freshness and hold windows for each source
3. HUD derives final mode and brightness floor
4. HUD publishes the effective HUD mode/brightness state
end note

@enduml
